{"tid":1877163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳國防部轉軚　同意加強封殺華為","createTime":"2020-02-13T00:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T02:14:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4834bd585d3409fe1112b0ba8aeabc66f5227995","tid":1877163,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"傳國防部轉軚　同意加強封殺華為<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200213/bkn-20200213063009985-0213_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200213%2Fbkn-20200213063009985-0213_00972_001.html&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=de2d8c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200213/bkn-20200213063009985-0213_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，美國防部一改早前態度，同意收緊對中國巨企華為的供貨限制，進一步封殺華為。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部在上月原本計劃發布一項規定，旨在進一步減少美國公司對華為供貨，但是國防部的研究及工程部提出反對，指這樣做會使美國的半導體公司難以保持業界的領導地位，同時這些公司的收入會因而減少，窒礙研製用於下一代戰機和其他武器的晶片。商務部因為國防部方面的反對，而將上述計劃擱置。<br />\n<br />\n但美國政治新聞網站Politico報道，國防部負責政策的次長魯德（John Rood）已經推翻了上述部門所提出的關注，改為支持加強封殺華為；這使得商務部得以推行令美國公司更難鑽空子向華為供貨的法規。據報政府將於稍後時間，開會商討更進一步限制向華為出口科技的措施。"},{"pid":"a100582c9d114a31a8f6e39a21ab9e0bbff2d000","tid":1877163,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822b83435e087038dfb15f27f2bf88f0fe42d14c","tid":1877163,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EBQcYWQWsAITjRs?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEBQcYWQWsAITjRs%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=f54e0705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6da598d061579d68f0cce13ea28f9226f664d7c","tid":1877163,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}